# 🎮Space Defender – Scratch Shooting Game#

## 🚀 Project Overview
This is a 2D shooting game built using Scratch (MIT platform).
The player controls a spaceship, shoots enemies, tracks score, and survives using a 3-life system.

## 🎯 Features
Player movement (left & right)
Shooting bullets using clones
Random enemy spawning
Score tracking system
3 Lives system
Game Over condition
Collision detection

## 🧠 Concepts Used
Variables (score, lives)
Clones
Loops (forever, repeat until)
Conditional statements
Operators (OR condition)
Event-driven programming

## 📂 File
Download .sb3 file and open in Scratch to play.
